Laku noć, Kerola.

00:36:55.740 --> 00:36:56.980
Hvala!

00:38:11.020 --> 00:38:13.820
Ne, ne, ne!
Šta je?

00:38:14.260 --> 00:38:16.020
Ne smeš to!

